Merge pull request #12 from elia/patch-1

Prefer Array#join over String#<<

Prefer Array#join over String#<<

Reasons:

1. @opal doesn't have mutable strings
2. Array#join is faster (see below)

```
Calculating -------------------------------------
             mutable     30801 i/100ms
                join     39253 i/100ms
-------------------------------------------------
             mutable   374769.7 (±2.4%) i/s -    3757722 in  10.032571s
                join   501529.1 (±5.2%) i/s -    5024384 in  10.051695s

Comparison:
                join:   501529.1 i/s
             mutable:   374769.7 i/s - 1.34x slower
```
